    <briefdescription>
<para>Abstract interface for theme-based color loading. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Platform or derived config implementations implement this interface. A concrete instance is created via UiConfigImpl::CreateThemeLoader().</para>
<para>The virtual method set is fixed for ABI stability. Future extensions should be added as non-virtual helper methods only. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
